<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَجْرٍ كَغُلَّانِ <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span> ... ...<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الخامس:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَرِيقَانِ:</span> مِنْهُمْ جَازِعٌ ... ...<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>البيتين <span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
